                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1289" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0175</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8906 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州茅台巨额货币资金与股东财富的关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The relationship between huge currency founds and shareholder wealth of Kweichow Moutai</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙成凤，闫庆友等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华北电力大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州茅台</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">货币资金；资产结构；资本结构；股东财富</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">currency founds; asset structure; capital structure; shareholder wealth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012年起，摧毁白酒股的各种利空从各处涌来。贵州茅台的股价从2012年7月16日的历史高点266.08元一路下跌，截止2013年4月26日，贵州茅台收盘价为173.99元，股东财富蒸发高达956.06亿元。2012年末贵州茅台持有高达220.62亿元货币资金，占资产总额的49.03%，年化收益率低于3个月银行定期存款利率。除了业务往来产生的应付项目外，贵州茅台没有债务。越来越多的投资者加入到了贵州茅台巨额货币资金与股东财富关系的讨论中。部分投资者认为贵州茅台的巨额货币资金有助于公司熬过白酒行业的冬天，而多数投资者却从不同角度认证了巨额货币资金已经损害了股东的财富。贵州茅台的管理层对巨额货币资金无明确的使用计划。贵州茅台无疑也是一家好公司，但从其股东价值的角度考虑，这样的资产结构和资本结构是否合理呢？如何解决公司巨额货币资金的烦恼才能使股东财富达到最大化？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2012, the negative signals of liquor stocks have come from everywhere. The price of Kweichow Moutai Moutai&#39;s stock dropped from the highest 266.08 yuan on July 16, 2012 to the closing price of 173.99 yuan on April 26, 2013, equaling a huge reduction of 95.606 billion yuan of its shareholder wealth. At the end of 2012, Kweichow Moutai held up to 22.062 billion yuan of currency funds, accounting for 49.03% of its total assets and the annual rate of return was lower than the three-month bank deposit rates. There was no liability except for accounts payable from daily business. More and more investors were arguing about the relationship between cash and shareholder wealth of Kweichow Moutai. There mainly held two points. Some of them said that money funds could lead the company to survive from the liquor industry depressions. While more people argued that the huge amount of currency had damaged shareholder wealth from many aspects. Also the management of Kweichow Moutai had no clear plan for the use of huge monetary funds. There is no doubt that Kweichow Moutai is a good company, but from the view of shareholder wealth, are the asset structure and capital structure reasonable? How to solve the problems of the huge amounts of cash to maximize shareholder wealth?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营运资本政策、货币资金管理、资本结构理论、财务管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1289" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
